reviewText: This product features a number of country music giants, some of them deceased, in their prime and singing some of their best known songs in the Austin City Limits setting.  It was fascinating to see these stars singing their best songs and feel a bit of sadness for the ones who passed on or do not have an active career any longer.  It was worth the price and the four star rating I gave it.  The color and clarity of the VHS tape format was very good, indeed.
